                    "value": "<p>Spiritbound Aluums are immune to spells and magical abilities, with two exceptions. A negative spell or magical ability grants an aluum enforcer the @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Quickened]{Quickened} condition until the end of its next turn instead of its normal effects. A positive spell or ability makes an Spiritbound Aluum @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Slowed]{Slowed} 1 until the end of its next turn instead of its normal effects.</p>"
