                "description": {
                    "chat": "",
                    "unidentified": "",
                    "value": "<p>A creature damaged by the Spirtibound Aluum's fist @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.Strike]{Strike} must succeed at a <span data-pf2-saving-throw=\"fortitude\" data-pf2-dc=\"35\" data-pf2-traits=\"arcane,incapacitation,necromancy\" data-pf2-label=\"Paralyzing Force DC\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Fortitude</span> save or become @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Paralyzed]{Paralyzed} for 1 round. On a critical failure, the creature is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Paralyzed]{Paralyzed} for [[/r 1d4]] minutes and falls @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Prone]{Prone}.</p>"
