                    "value": "<p><strong>Requirements</strong>: The spiritbound aluum has bound a soul using its @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Bind Soul]{Bind Soul} innate spell;</p>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong>: The spiritbound aluum transforms the captured soul's essence into raw magical energy, channeling the spirit into a beam that deals [[/r 20d6 #force]] force damage in a 30-foot line (<span data-pf2-saving-throw=\"reflex\" data-pf2-dc=\"38\" data-pf2-traits=\"arcane,evocation,force,damaging-effect\" data-pf2-label=\"Obliteration Beam DC\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">basic Reflex</span> save). The remaining fragments of the captured soul are released to the Great Beyond. The spiritbound aluum can't use Obliteration Beam again for [[/r 1d4]] rounds.</p>"
