                },
                "description": {
                    "chat": "",
                    "unidentified": "",
                    "value": "<p>The aluum enforcer emits a keening wail in a 15-foot cone that deals [[/r 16d6 # sonic]] sonic damage (<span data-pf2-saving-throw=\"fortitude\" data-pf2-dc=\"27\" data-pf2-traits=\"arcane,auditory,evocation,mental,sonic,damaging-effect\" data-pf2-label=\"Soul Shriek DC\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">basic Fortitude</span> save). A creature that fails its save is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Stunned]{Stunned} 1, or @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Stunned]{Stunned} 3 on a critical failure. The aluum can't use Soul Shriek again for [[/r 1d4]] rounds.</p>"
                },
